						<v8:item>
							<v8:lang>en</v8:lang>
							<v8:content>Implementation of works (services) performed (rendered) by organizations of pipeline transport of oil and oil products, transportation, handling and (or) an overload of petroleum products placed under the customs procedure of customs transit, as well as exported from the territory of the Russian Federation on the territory of the State - a member of the Customs Union</v8:content>
						</v8:item>
					</tl>
				</c>
			</c>
