							<v8:lang>en</v8:lang>
							<v8:content>The implementation of an autonomous non-profit organization established in accordance with the Federal Law "On Protection of interests of individuals who have deposits in banks, and separate structural subdivisions of banks registered and (or) acts on the territory of the Republic of Crimea and the territory of the federal city of Sevastopol", property and property rights and the provision of services by the organization on representation of interests of investors</v8:content>
