							<v8:content>Sales of goods (works and services), except for excisable goods sold (performed, rendered) in the provision of grant aid (assistance) to the Russian Federation in accordance with the Federal Law "About the gratuitous aid (assistance) of the Russian Federation and the Introduction of Amendments and Additions to Certain Legislative acts of the Russian Federation on taxes and the establishment of advantageous contributions to state extrabudgetary funds in connection with the grant aid (assistance) of the Russian Federation "</v8:content>
